name: Rogue [X-men]
description:
Rogue - X-men

Nah this one's not for pride, unless -- y'know you want it to be LOL. I'm sure she'd punch a facist or two in the nuts.

Anyways, this is the 2nd time trying to do rogue, and we realized one major mistake this time:

DO NOT MIX ALL OF HER OUTFITS IN ONE LORA.

IT WILL CONSISTENTLY TRY AND DO HER CLASSIC ONE.

Also tag absorbtion is a bitch only use it for hair and eyes.

Classic was MEANT TO: Invoke her CLASSIC OUTFIT
What it does do: In the words of Arin Hanson: ABSOLUTE G-D BULLSHIZ F*CK XD
Southern Bell: Mostly ... i ... HAVE NO. CLUE ANYMORE TEST IT AND SEE It was meant to keep her hair and eyes

Rogue: Probably does most of the work because I think we messed up and misspelled rogue and had to reset it.

Superhero: I HAVE NO CLUE And try not to uise this one too much or you get stupid poses.

Xtreme: THIS IN THEORY MIXED WITH invoking her actual colors of the outfit are from the 2000's Salvador Larocca on pencils "X-TREME X-MEN" - However, it still hates me and refuses to do it entirely.

Savage: IT WAS MEANT TO DO SAVAGE LAND ROGUE - Ignore this tag, go get the horny one that we didn't make for this LMAO.

WHAT YOU DO NEED TO KNOW: IT CAN DO AN AESTHETIC of 80s Rogue, and an AESTHETIC of the "HIGH SCHOOL GOTH" rogue from Evolution. It just didn't have enough data to do that outfit specifically.
